snippet.title: Lil' Howie's Fun House Intro
snippet.description:
The intro to a CD-Rom game from my Childhood Lil' Howie's Fun House staring Howie Mandel 
I never played the Great Math Adventure but I have fond Childhood Memories from The Great Word Adventure
